{"tid":2500432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以色列特工潛入伊朗核設施放炸彈後全身而退 預計伊朗核設施最少需要九個月修復","createTime":"2021-04-22T15:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T18:51:43.000Z","uid":391580,"like":224,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"f0aef96e50bb4f8d142e02bc6420285a80968f67","tid":2500432,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:24:14.000Z","msg":"媒體報道，伊朗情報部門已經確認了襲擊伊朗納坦茲地下核設施的主犯姓名和照片。伊朗情報部門發現，襲擊伊朗地下核基地的主犯就是特工裏紮&middot;卡裏米。正是這個人將炸彈帶進了伊朗核設施，安裝在了伊朗核設施的供電系統上。導致伊朗核設施發生爆炸，要9個月時間才能完全恢複。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNxu7CmjZkT5Fz6wi4P5Enoa23Ds9ocVxGgsdWozWxWjK?filename=KzrQSg4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzrQSg4.jpg&h=c173f348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據情報，現在這名特工已經逃離伊朗，伊朗外交部長紮裏夫對此表示，以色列是攻擊的幕後黑手，伊朗&ldquo;將進行報複&rdquo;。同時，伊朗情報部門表示，他們還掌握了其他很多信息，現在，伊朗正在追蹤這些破壞分子。24小時不停歇地追蹤，一定要抓捕到他們。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZZeNbThQSytq42d6brRWKQQSdrExngjf2DcPYkFCeG8m?filename=FAnHJoR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFAnHJoR.jpg&h=3c772aaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據伊朗IFP新聞網4月17日報道，伊朗報紙《開漢日報》提出對以色列的迪莫納核反應堆實施打擊。以回應以色列&ldquo;對伊朗納坦茲核設施的破壞行為。&rdquo;以色列在1年時間，已經2次襲擊了伊朗核設施，一次在爆炸了離心機，一次是爆炸了供電系統。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfF3JSRrqotctKKnxf2oMxXkp8dCofDErfu4JQaY1kDRW?filename=Q5oDgJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ5oDgJY.jpg&h=fb552766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伊朗前原子能機構負責人費雷頓&middot;阿巴斯-達瓦尼表示這一次遭到襲擊的是位于地下50米的核設施變電站，襲擊者將炸彈偷偷帶進核基地。隨後遠程引爆炸彈，摧毀了核電站的主要和預備電力系統。但是還不知道，裏紮&middot;卡裏米是怎麼把炸彈帶進伊朗戒備森嚴的核設施的。<br />\n<br />\n最大的可能就是障眼法，在2020年7月，以色列特工將炸彈藏進了家具裏，帶進了伊朗核基地炸毀了部分新型離心機。這一次很可能采用的是一個方法。不得不說，裏紮&middot;卡裏米的能力非常强，可以一個人帶着炸彈進入層層警衛和嚴密檢查的伊朗地下核基地。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSVdT39PHkVVvUfwcTLjvh1xwhoHu92Vf41dEBsRgPwco?filename=kUivSht.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkUivSht.jpg&h=bc10cbca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隨後神不知鬼不覺地將炸彈安裝在了最關鍵位置上，再安全地離開現場。甚至躲過了層層檢查和追捕，在第一時間逃離了伊朗。在4月11日，伊朗宣布新型離心機投入使用，在4月12日淩晨4點，隱藏在伊朗核基地的炸彈爆炸了！伊朗感到了恥辱和憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n這不是第一次，也不會是最後一次，以色列還會繼續襲擊伊朗核設施。因為，以色列人肯定已經掌握了伊朗核基地的所有秘密。因為，伊朗官員表示，&ldquo;從科技的角度講，敵人的設計非常完美，爆炸裝置設法損壞配電系統和通向離心機的電纜，從而切斷離心機的電源。&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeaAGewjtbBLuDoyrxoXCFv1KoGxEP7j9agBUc1zHpfZh?filename=BH7wBKe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBH7wBKe.jpg&h=fbccb921&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n那麼問題是，以色列摩薩德是怎麼清楚地知道，伊朗核基地的各個關鍵部位的位置？而且還可以為特工設計出一條可以在基地裏躲避各種探測監控系統的路線？<br />\n<br />\n從2020年7月，第一次襲擊伊朗核基地，到年底暗殺伊朗首席核科學家法赫裏-紮德，再到今年4月，爆炸伊朗地下核基地供電系統。以色列摩薩德的行動能力，策劃能力讓人驚歎不已。而且幾次行動的襲擊者，全部都安全撤離，全身而退。這種行動和計劃能力，更是讓人贊歎不已。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeGqeFLwDyansPs64L4HwSnEYgPsY99F6fVsB1uJT5EWa?filename=qEFqGa1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqEFqGa1.jpg&h=1c9781ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現在，伊朗已經公開了潛入伊朗地下核基地布設炸彈的以色列特工的照片。就是這個人，執行了這一次絕對是驚天級的襲擊行動。滲透進隱藏在沙漠地區的伊朗核設施，躲避開不知道多少警衛和視頻紅外監控系統，進入到了伊朗核基地地下50米的核心部位安裝炸彈。隨後又安全撤離，逃出伊朗！拿着獎金，現在不知道在哪裏正在快樂逍遙呢！"},{"pid":"d47f1e9d828cc3bfad32517c2ff8688c31a0b8a9","tid":2500432,"uid":3063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:25:53.000Z","msg":"007"},{"pid":"228cf9f887b16ab23a00303f8ed08d8a0838d242","tid":2500432,"uid":161863,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:29:21.000Z","msg":"下集職業特工隊"},{"pid":"8b2ba71fdf80f2b676120a3fead88090aef2f94d","tid":2500432,"uid":52215,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"咁撚高調，轉個頭俾人隊冧啦"},{"pid":"8929abcd78436d65757036d5364bb69a73029e05","tid":2500432,"uid":235152,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"殺手47"},{"pid":"2ef9d2192cbd68619dd3eb6c9960ee21fbecbb80","tid":2500432,"uid":391580,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:30:51.000Z","msg":"伊朗核設施大爆炸 電力網全當 官方控遭恐怖攻擊<br />\n12:36      2021/04/12<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20210412002415-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20210412002415-260408&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrfY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=5905e3f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20210412002415-260408</a>"},{"pid":"78858079842033a1de13e51b1263fd26576dc1d8","tid":2500432,"uid":7524,"like":41,"dislike":5,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"8b2ba71fdf80f2b676120a3fead88090aef2f94d","tid":2500432,"uid":52215,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"咁撚高調，轉個頭俾人隊冧啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:31:01.000Z","msg":"國家級保護， 易左容嘆緊世界"},{"pid":"1944a21a25341989064b4a84f2851bcd3dc4a0e3","tid":2500432,"uid":87073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:31:03.000Z","msg":"譚雅"},{"pid":"5ce199c380f9587ea8565e0058ed637f9b7c2092","tid":2500432,"uid":215634,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"quote":{"pid":"8b2ba71fdf80f2b676120a3fead88090aef2f94d","tid":2500432,"uid":52215,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"咁撚高調，轉個頭俾人隊冧啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:31:04.000Z","msg":"個樣分分鐘係假，特工要喬裝整容有幾難？"},{"pid":"0d3c74f20489ae41b7f093db3817d87ad36cc6ab","tid":2500432,"uid":14494,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:31:55.000Z","msg":"傻仔伊朗聽左習大大老點走去打猶太佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你睇俄佬依家都退兵"},{"pid":"09b5369db8d97b05be8ce14baa4a2375a8da70db","tid":2500432,"uid":176447,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:32:14.000Z","msg":"plot twist 伊朗自己柒咗屈個dissenter係特工"},{"pid":"3bc6b1f9478d8f8610093f69a914a25e134f567e","tid":2500432,"uid":34295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:32:52.000Z","msg":"好堅<br />\n幾時還拖"},{"pid":"2a81178af7364cb16900253df16e07b636d80ddd","tid":2500432,"uid":34047,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:33:02.000Z","msg":"諗起red alert 2"},{"pid":"d33cc1ac38b84beef30fd372a24041c1489e6fbd","tid":2500432,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d469e890f4af7c97e906453fb38c665b8077467","tid":2500432,"uid":114781,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:38:58.000Z","msg":"以色列見廢燈上去又要傾又盛都廢鳩事睬佢，自己郁手先<br />\n廢燈種廢真係唔講得笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c1577cd4664228497315c150f471e0d5fa7cce","tid":2500432,"uid":295230,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"8b2ba71fdf80f2b676120a3fead88090aef2f94d","tid":2500432,"uid":52215,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"咁撚高調，轉個頭俾人隊冧啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:42:37.000Z","msg":"就係睇死佢無能力係以色列保護下搵到呢條友"},{"pid":"909261803b7cffd99e85d5875d52c77dd990c622","tid":2500432,"uid":237562,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"8d469e890f4af7c97e906453fb38c665b8077467","tid":2500432,"uid":114781,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:38:58.000Z","msg":"以色列見廢燈上去又要傾又盛都廢鳩事睬佢，自己郁手先<br />\n廢燈種廢真係唔講得笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:43:49.000Z","msg":"講眞以色列咁聽美國話嘅<br />\n<br />\n當初都唔打六日戰爭啦"},{"pid":"d71e49